{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/issue/004-pickk-app-reject/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"최수민 개발 블로그","siteUrl":"https://sumini.dev"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d8b2b8ce-5463-5c2f-a846-56267396754e","excerpt":"최근 개발중인 PICKK 앱이 조만간 플레이스토어/앱스토어 출시를 앞두고 있습니다. iOS 심사가 까다롭기로 소문나서 걱정했는데, 리젝 사유가 명확하고 피드백이 빨라 무난했습니다 :) PICKK iOS 앱스토어 리젝 사유와 해결한 방법에 대해서 간단하게 정리해보겠습니다. 1. Apple…","html":"<p>최근 개발중인 PICKK 앱이 조만간 플레이스토어/앱스토어 출시를 앞두고 있습니다.</p>\n<p>iOS 심사가 까다롭기로 소문나서 걱정했는데, 리젝 사유가 명확하고 피드백이 빨라 무난했습니다 :)</p>\n<p>PICKK iOS 앱스토어 리젝 사유와 해결한 방법에 대해서 간단하게 정리해보겠습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-apple로-로그인-텍스트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-apple%EB%A1%9C-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"1 apple로 로그인 텍스트 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Apple로 로그인 (텍스트)</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAZ0lEQVQY06VOWwpFIRCa/S+26EHv8OCAEPf3BqaJzWg5Z4QQUEpBSsn5n2NjDLTW0HsHNXmthb23s7Qg782IzzkwNooxejuBjQn65FqrL3uXvwWEOSeMF4cqLNBjiFofxb9D9b734gMiYjhANM+TIQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sign-in-with-apple-text\"\n        title=\"sign-in-with-apple-text\"\n        src=\"/static/0e64b78b0da2911b3973b85a209060c0/5a190/sign-in-with-apple-text.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0e64b78b0da2911b3973b85a209060c0/772e8/sign-in-with-apple-text.png 200w,\n/static/0e64b78b0da2911b3973b85a209060c0/e17e5/sign-in-with-apple-text.png 400w,\n/static/0e64b78b0da2911b3973b85a209060c0/5a190/sign-in-with-apple-text.png 800w,\n/static/0e64b78b0da2911b3973b85a209060c0/a4262/sign-in-with-apple-text.png 814w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>애플 로그인 버튼의 텍스트를 <code class=\"language-text\">애플 계정으로 시작하기</code>로 했었는데, <code class=\"language-text\">Apple로 로그인</code>으로 바꿔야만한다고 합니다. 😅</p>\n<p>이외에도 애플 로그인 버튼의 디자인은 애플에서 제시한 여러 규칙들을 지켜야합니다. 자세한 내용은 <a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/sign-in-with-apple/overview/buttons/\">Human Interface Guidelines</a> 참고</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"2-apple로-로그인-데이터\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-apple%EB%A1%9C-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0\" aria-label=\"2 apple로 로그인 데이터 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Apple로 로그인 (데이터)</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 27%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAFCAYAAABFA8wzAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAgElEQVQY022PCQpEIQxDvf9p3TfQDk/IR2SE2No2aXSlFEsp2RjDaq0feu9GL+d8IrUY46lz9t72nrWWOQgCwsohIyRReq21I0hkgRZpDjguyK+wasT7Pec8orjB5Y3jkCbDIor8CukdQjgO/32ZmhOJwTsqBxK8lwLv/TcDMPcDUp2Dx0gA+KYAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sign-in-with-apple-data\"\n        title=\"sign-in-with-apple-data\"\n        src=\"/static/f0515595f969375dcc105587782380cb/5a190/sign-in-with-apple-data.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0515595f969375dcc105587782380cb/772e8/sign-in-with-apple-data.png 200w,\n/static/f0515595f969375dcc105587782380cb/e17e5/sign-in-with-apple-data.png 400w,\n/static/f0515595f969375dcc105587782380cb/5a190/sign-in-with-apple-data.png 800w,\n/static/f0515595f969375dcc105587782380cb/b4098/sign-in-with-apple-data.png 816w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>애플 로그인을 통해 인증된 유저에게 이메일/전화번호 등의 추가 정보를 수집하지 말라고 합니다.</p>\n<p>유저들에 대한 확실한 연락 수단을 위해 수집하고 있었는데, 애플 연동 유저에게만 수집하지 않도록 바꿔야만 했습니다.. 😥</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"3-권한-요청-메세지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EA%B6%8C%ED%95%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%B2%AD-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%B8%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"3 권한 요청 메세지 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25