bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gallery-notice-example\"\n        title=\"gallery-notice-example\"\n        src=\"/static/b62c2e1d21645caad86d1856828b5894/f7a31/gallery-notice-example.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b62c2e1d21645caad86d1856828b5894/772e8/gallery-notice-example.png 200w,\n/static/b62c2e1d21645caad86d1856828b5894/e17e5/gallery-notice-example.png 400w,\n/static/b62c2e1d21645caad86d1856828b5894/f7a31/gallery-notice-example.png 458w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 458px) 100vw, 458px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>사진 접근 권한 요청시 안내 문구를 명시하라는 내용입니다. 위와 같이 사용됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>key</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>key</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>카메라 롤에서 선택한 사진을 올려 공유할 수 있습니다.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Info.plist에 위 내용을 추가해서 해결할 수 있었습니다.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-apple%EB%A1%9C-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\">1. Apple로 로그인 (텍스트)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-apple%EB%A1%9C-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%